data.description: **Motivated Seller!! **  This immaculate single-story house, located on a quiet cul-de-sac, has an ideal layout. It boasts 1,720 sqf, 3 good-sized bedrooms, a den, 2 full bathrooms, tile flooring throughout, and a 2-car garage with an extra 4 feet space. Huge open-concept kitchen, dining / living room, granite countertop, and an oversized pantry. The master bedroom is large and bright, and master bathroom includes dual vanities, a large shower, as well as a large walk-in closet. The easy-care backyard has a covered patio recently extended, with a brand-new aluminum pergola, and outdoor kitchen, with granite countertops. The BBQ Grill has NEVER been used. It is a perfect spot to relax and take in the sunset and mountain views.
